Map:map_PK_port_linhir/Desc
"Situated at the south of the Gondor, in the confluence of Gilrain and Serni rivers, Linhir is a port city known by its opulent market and services. During the War of the Ring a clash between Invasors of Umbar and Aragorn's Dead Army took place. In the 4th age a new oligarchy mix of a local gondorian lords and a new burguesy from harad is governing the city. \n Map by Powerkartoffel"
End
